<h1 class="govuk-heading-l">How can the service engage with the people who need support?</h1>

<p>Let the service know the best way to engage with them, such as:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>best time and day to contact</li>
    <li>preferred method for contact</li>
    <li>communication needs such as an interpreter or textphone</li>
    <li>any restrictions on how they can send and receive calls or texts</li>
</ul>